OL,3,CMan due in court after house explosion
OL,4,Cin Lancashire
OL,6,FA man has been charged with arson with
OL,7,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,8,Fendangered after a house explosion in
OL,9,FLancashire.
OL,11,FDarren Davies, 54, of Carr Lane,
OL,12,FHambleton will appear at Lancaster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 30 March.
OL,15,FNeighbours say they heard "an almighty
OL,16,Fbang" in the usually quiet village of
OL,17,FHambleton, in Lancashire, just before
OL,18,F9.55am on 27 March, before discovering
OL,19,Fthe explosion and fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
