PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774897908
OL,3,CMan due in court after house explosion
OL,4,Cin Lancashire
OL,6,FEmergency Services were called, and a
OL,7,F54-year-old man was taken to hospital
OL,8,Fwith minor injuries, North West
OL,9,FAmbulance Service said. No one else
OL,10,Fhad been injured.
OL,12,FLancashire Police said it was being
OL,13,Ftreated as an "isolated incident".
OL,15,FEngineers from both Electricity North
OL,16,FWest and Cadent, which manages the gas
OL,17,Fnetwork, were called to the scene
OL,18,Fafter the explosion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
