PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774897908
OL,3,CMan due in court after house explosion
OL,4,Cin Lancashire
OL,6,FCadent has since confirmed the
OL,7,Fexplosion is not directly linked to
OL,8,Fthe gas network staff are on scene to
OL,9,Fmake the area safe.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Lancashire Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "Shortly before 9:55am on Friday
OL,13,F27 March, we received a report from
OL,14,Fthe fire service of a fire at a
OL,15,Fproperty on Carr Lane, Hambleton.
OL,17,FAs part of our investigation we have
OL,18,Fnow charged a man."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
